library AWATestComposite version '0.0.008'

using QDM version '5.4'

include CompositeFunctions version '0.1.000' called Composite
include AnnualWellnessAssessmentPreventiveCarePneumococcalVaccination version '0.4.000' called ComponentMeasurePneumococcal
include AnnualWellnessAssessmentPreventiveCareScreeningforColorectalCancer version '0.4.000' called ComponentMeasureColorectal
include AnnualWellnessAssessmentPreventiveCareScreeningforDepression version '0.4.000' called ComponentMeasureDepression
include AnnualWellnessAssessmentPreventiveCareScreeningforFallsRisk version '0.4.000' called ComponentMeasureFalls
include AnnualWellnessAssessmentPreventiveCareScreeningforOsteoporosis version '0.4.000' called ComponentMeasureOsteoporosis
include AnnualWellnessAssessmentPreventiveCareInfluenzaVaccination version '0.4.000' called ComponentMeasureInfluenza
include AnnualWellnessAssessmentPreventiveCareScreeningforBreastCancer version '0.5.000' called ComponentMeasureBreast

valueset "Ethnicity": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.114222.4.11.837'
valueset "ONC Administrative Sex": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113762.1.4.1'
valueset "Payer": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.114222.4.11.3591'
valueset "Race": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.114222.4.11.836'

context Patient

define "SDE Ethnicity":
	["Patient Characteristic Ethnicity": "Ethnicity"]

define "SDE Payer":
	["Patient Characteristic Payer": "Payer"]

define "SDE Race":
	["Patient Characteristic Race": "Race"]

define "SDE Sex":
	["Patient Characteristic Sex": "ONC Administrative Sex"]

define "Is In ComponentMeasurePneumococcal Denominator":
	ComponentMeasurePneumococcal."Initial Population"
		and ComponentMeasurePneumococcal."Denominator"
		and not ComponentMeasurePneumococcal."Denominator Exclusions"

define "Is In ComponentMeasurePneumococcal Numerator":
	ComponentMeasurePneumococcal."Initial Population"
		and ComponentMeasurePneumococcal."Denominator"
		and not ComponentMeasurePneumococcal."Denominator Exclusions"
		and ComponentMeasurePneumococcal."Numerator"

define "Is In ComponentMeasureColorectal Numerator":
	ComponentMeasureColorectal."Initial Population"
		and ComponentMeasureColorectal."Denominator"
		and not ComponentMeasureColorectal."Denominator Exclusions"
		and ComponentMeasureColorectal."Numerator"

define "Is In ComponentMeasureDepression Numerator":
	ComponentMeasureDepression."Initial Population"
		and ComponentMeasureDepression."Denominator"
		and not ComponentMeasureDepression."Denominator Exclusions"
		and ComponentMeasureDepression."Numerator"

define "Is In ComponentMeasureFalls Denominator":
	ComponentMeasureFalls."Initial Population"
		and ComponentMeasureFalls."Denominator"
		and not ComponentMeasureFalls."Denominator Exclusions"

define "Is In ComponentMeasureFalls Numerator":
	ComponentMeasureFalls."Initial Population"
		and ComponentMeasureFalls."Denominator"
		and not ComponentMeasureFalls."Denominator Exclusions"
		and ComponentMeasureFalls."Numerator"

define "Is In ComponentMeasureInfluenza Denominator":
	ComponentMeasureInfluenza."Initial Population"
		and ComponentMeasureInfluenza."Denominator"
		and not ( ComponentMeasureInfluenza."Denominator Exceptions"
				and not ComponentMeasureInfluenza."Numerator"
		)

define "Is In ComponentMeasureInfluenza Numerator":
	ComponentMeasureInfluenza."Initial Population"
		and ComponentMeasureInfluenza."Denominator"
		and ComponentMeasureInfluenza."Numerator"

define "Is In ComponentMeasureOsteoporosis Denominator":
	ComponentMeasureOsteoporosis."Initial Population"
		and ComponentMeasureOsteoporosis."Denominator"
		and not ComponentMeasureOsteoporosis."Denominator Exclusions"

define "Is In ComponentMeasureOsteoporosis Numerator":
	ComponentMeasureOsteoporosis."Initial Population"
		and ComponentMeasureOsteoporosis."Denominator"
		and not ComponentMeasureOsteoporosis."Denominator Exclusions"
		and ComponentMeasureOsteoporosis."Numerator"

define "Is In ComponentMeasureColorectal Denominator":
	ComponentMeasureColorectal."Initial Population"
		and ComponentMeasureColorectal."Denominator"
		and not ComponentMeasureColorectal."Denominator Exclusions"

define "Is In ComponentMeasureDepression Denominator":
	ComponentMeasureDepression."Initial Population"
		and ComponentMeasureDepression."Denominator"
		and not ComponentMeasureDepression."Denominator Exclusions"
		and not ( ComponentMeasureDepression."Denominator Exceptions"
				and not ComponentMeasureDepression."Numerator"
		)

define "Is In ComponentMeasureBreast Denominator":
	ComponentMeasureBreast."Initial Population"
		and ComponentMeasureBreast."Denominator"
		and not ComponentMeasureBreast."Denominator Exclusions"

define "Is In ComponentMeasureBreast Numerator":
	ComponentMeasureBreast."Initial Population"
		and ComponentMeasureBreast."Denominator"
		and not ComponentMeasureBreast."Denominator Exclusions"
		and ComponentMeasureBreast."Numerator"

define "Initial Population":
	["Patient Characteristic Birthdate"] Pt
		where ComponentMeasurePneumococcal."Initial Population"
			or ComponentMeasureColorectal."Initial Population"
			or ComponentMeasureDepression."Initial Population"
			or ComponentMeasureFalls."Initial Population"
			or ComponentMeasureOsteoporosis."Initial Population"
			or ComponentMeasureInfluenza."Initial Population"
			or ComponentMeasureBreast."Initial Population"

define "Measure Population":
	["Patient Characteristic Birthdate"] Pt
		where ComponentMeasurePneumococcal."Denominator"
			or ComponentMeasureColorectal."Denominator"
			or ComponentMeasureDepression."Denominator"
			or ComponentMeasureFalls."Denominator"
			or ComponentMeasureOsteoporosis."Denominator"
			or ComponentMeasureInfluenza."Denominator"
			or ComponentMeasureBreast."Denominator"

define "Numerator Score":
	Composite.ToScore("Is In ComponentMeasurePneumococcal Numerator")+ Composite.ToScore("Is In ComponentMeasureColorectal Numerator")+ Composite.ToScore("Is In ComponentMeasureDepression Numerator")+ Composite.ToScore("Is In ComponentMeasureFalls Numerator")+ Composite.ToScore("Is In ComponentMeasureOsteoporosis Numerator")+ Composite.ToScore("Is In ComponentMeasureInfluenza Numerator")+ Composite.ToScore("Is In ComponentMeasureBreast Numerator")

define "Denominator Score":
	Composite.ToScore("Is In ComponentMeasurePneumococcal Denominator")+ Composite.ToScore("Is In ComponentMeasureColorectal Denominator")+ Composite.ToScore("Is In ComponentMeasureDepression Denominator")+ Composite.ToScore("Is In ComponentMeasureFalls Denominator")+ Composite.ToScore("Is In ComponentMeasureOsteoporosis Denominator")+ Composite.ToScore("Is In ComponentMeasureInfluenza Denominator")+ Composite.ToScore("Is In ComponentMeasureBreast Denominator")

define "Measure Population Exclusions":
	["Patient Characteristic Birthdate"] Pt
		where ComponentMeasurePneumococcal."Denominator Exclusions"
			and ComponentMeasureColorectal."Denominator Exclusions"
			and ComponentMeasureDepression."Denominator Exclusions"
			and ComponentMeasureFalls."Denominator Exclusions"
			and ComponentMeasureOsteoporosis."Denominator Exclusions"
			and ComponentMeasureBreast."Denominator Exclusions"

define function "Measure Observation"(patient "Patient Characteristic Birthdate"):
	"Numerator Score" / "Denominator Score"
